item.title: CVE-2021-36336|2024-08-04T00:54:51.391Z -- dell -- wyse%20management%20suite
item.description: Wyse Management Suite 3.3.1 and below versions contain a deserialization vulnerability that could allow an unauthenticated attacker to execute code on the affected system.

item.title: CVE-2021-36337|2024-08-04T00:54:51.461Z -- dell -- wyse%20management%20suite
item.description: Dell Wyse Management Suite version 3.3.1 and prior support insecure Transport Security Protocols TLS 1.0 and TLS 1.1 which are susceptible to Man-In-The-Middle attacks thereby compromising Confidentiality and Integrity of data.
